# Convex Production Backups
# ZIP files are gitignored (contain user data)
#
# Filename format: prod-{commitHash}-{clean|dirty}-{timestamp}.zip
#   Example: prod-abc123f-clean-20260123_191500.zip
#
# Commands:
#   npm run backup:prod   - Create timestamped backup (no deploy)
#   npm run deploy:safe   - Backup + deploy (recommended)
#
# Restore:
#   npx convex import --prod ./backups/<filename>.zip
#
# Keeps last 5 backups, older ones auto-deleted
